text: Kenneth Otto Eikenberry (born June 29, 1932) is an American Republican politician. He was born in Wenatchee, Washington. Eikenberry was the Attorney General of Washington from January 1981 through January 1993. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1932 births Category:Living people Category:Lawyers from Washington (state) Category:Politicians from Washington (state) Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
